ource/Club_Atl\\u00e9tico_Lan\\u00fas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Club_Atl\\u00e9tico_Lan\\u00fas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although they face competition from several top clubs, Soler is seen as an ideal fit for Slot's team.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Should Liverpool successfully secure Soler, Robertson would still remain the first-choice left-back.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1344, \"end\": 1353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.29968522450694e-22, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Robertson\", \"score\": 0.707520754624907, \"rank\": 0.41338609957435235, \"text\": \"Robertson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Robertson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Robertson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the long-term plan would be for the Argentine to eventually take over the role.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999928137416562, \"rank\": 7.1858181805123145e-06, \"text\": \"Argentine\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is understood that Lanus would be open to a deal around the \\u00a313 million mark for the teenager which is relative pocket change for Liverpool and makes a deal doable.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end