re everybody is looking at.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But players stayed fit and they are able to perform in the way we want, so [a] high-intensity game.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"We saw some great goals during this tour, some great build-up situations and I see them working really, really hard not to concede.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like I said, today I think we gave away too many chances, United deserved more than a 3-0 loss.\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's also our quality that we do score our own chances.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We need to work hard in the upcoming two weeks to be ready for Ipswich.\\\"\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2967, \"end\": 2974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ipswich_Town_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.0830846911907605e-12, \"text\": \"Ipswich\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ipswich_Town_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ipswich_Town_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 3147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3115, \"end\": 3128, \"title\": \"http://dbp